</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="69.[151,1437,151,250]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">
Geographic distribution. Mediterranean and Atlantic Ocean. In the Mediterranean, known from the northern coast from Alboran Sea to Levant, and also on the south coast from 
<collectingCountry box="[911,995,187,213]" name="Algeria" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">Algeria</collectingCountry>
(Miller 1986). In the Atlantic Ocean, it was recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[368,469,223,249]" name="Morocco" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">Morocco</collectingCountry>
and Canaries (Miller 1986).
</paragraph>
